    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span>&nbsp;<strong>vegetable stock cube</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[180ml]</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>classic basil nut pesto</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> and mix to combine &ndash; this is your <strong>creamy&nbsp;pesto sauce</strong></p>",
